        walkthrough = '1. Start the quest by talking to Yurim at (J-8) in Tavnazian Safehold on the top floor.\n2. Choose a reward, then trade the appropriate base item and chip to Yurim. Be careful as you cannot cancel the quest after making your decision!\n3. Speak to Yurim again. You can either go farm the appropriate EX items now or you can trade an Apple Pie to Yurim for a hint.\n   - I\'d suggest saving the money and just using the table below.\n4. Trade the appropriate items to Yurim to complete the quest and receive your reward.\n5. Completing the quest once by obtaining any 1 item allows you to trade vices and auras dropped from several HNMs in Lumoria to Meret for a reward.\n6.  Silver Earring\n7.  Black Chip\n8. 5  Euvhi Organ\n9. 5  Luminian Tissue\n10.  Silver Earring\n11.  White Chip\n12. 5  Euvhi Organ\n13. 5  Luminian Tissue\n14.  Silver Obi\n15.  Red Chip\n16. 7  Phuabo Organ\n17. 3  Xzomit Organ\n18. 3  Luminian Tissue\n19.  Silver Obi\n20.  Yellow Chip\n21. 7  Hpemde Organ\n22. 3  Aern Organ\n23. 3  Luminian Tissue\n24.  Silver Obi\n25.  Blue Chip\n26. 7  Hpemde Organ\n27. 3  Phuabo Organ\n28. 3  Luminian Tissue\n29.  Silver Obi\n30.  Green Chip\n31. 7  Aern Organ\n32. 3  Hpemde Organ\n33. 3  Luminian Tissue\n34.  Silver Obi\n35.  Clear Chip\n36. 7  Xzomit Organ\n37. 3  Phuabo Organ\n38. 3  Luminian Tissue\n39.  Silver Obi\n40.  Purple Chip\n41. 7  Phuabo Organ\n42. 3  Hpemde Organ\n43. 3  Luminian Tissue\n44.  Silver Obi\n45.  White Chip\n46. 7  Xzomit Organ\n47. 3  Aern Organ\n48. 3  Luminian Tissue\n49.  Silver Obi\n50.  Black Chip\n51. 7  Aern Organ\n52. 3  Xzomit Organ\n53. 3  Luminian Tissue\n54.  Gorget\n55.  Red Chip\n56. 10  Phuabo Organ\n57. 5  Xzomit Organ\n58. 1  Yovra Organ\n59.  Gorget\n60.  Yellow Chip\n61. 10  Xzomit Organ\n62. 5  Aern Organ\n63. 1  Yovra Organ\n64.  Gorget\n65.  Blue Chip\n66. 10  Aern Organ\n67. 5  Hpemde Organ\n68. 1  Yovra Organ\n69.  Gorget\n70.  Green Chip\n71. 10  Phuabo Organ\n72. 5  Hpemde Organ\n73. 1  Yo