        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Leporaitceau (J-8) in the underground of the 3rd floor.\n   - Home Point #3 is closest.\n2. Speak to Equette (I-9) on the 2nd floor near the bottom of the ramp.\n3. Speak to Anteurephiaux (J-8) on the 3rd floor near Leporaitceau to officially begin this quest.\n4. Travel to Misareaux Coast and look for a ??? at (K-12).\n5. Checking the ??? will spawn the NM Bloody Coffin.\n   - Bloody Coffin has very damage reduction except for when it is casting spells.\n   - When it casts spells its damage reduction drops dramatically.\n6. Once the NM is defeated, check the ??? again for the [Key Item]Whispering conch.\n7. Return to Anteurephiaux.\n8. Finally, speak to Equette to complete this quest.',
